{"tid":1471021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終極文宣既誕生 升呢學新技","createTime":"2019-08-14T07:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:03:41.000Z","uid":285274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2af3a7699e34af5a4eb11f42f6ba837a7db738e","tid":1471021,"uid":285274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"Sor9myNameIsP牌仔<br />\n原諒我只係近排先覺醒既香港人 not9<br />\n所以仲未甩到牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為之前發太多次加上身體差<br />\n哮喘底同蠶豆症（多數化學野都GG）<br />\n搞到依幾日都霖左<br />\n又柯又嘔又發冷汗又暈（吊 總言之好撚多）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好可惜尋日唔發夢齋睇直播<br />\n見到啲9既做法 （重點黎）<br />\n為左救一兩個支那仔而大派人手 <br />\n平時已經唔見佢派咁多<br />\n點解一搞支那仔即刻派咁多人 <br />\n仲要係快閃 黎一陣就走 咁浪費狗力 心諗無解</span><br />\n<br />\n直到岩岩睇左<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對家做法</span></strong><br />\n原來啲狗只係為左文宣先咁大費周章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面有對家啲攻勢 慎入 可能造成憤怒可能洗埋On9仔腦 所以唔好亂傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8VTNg4tiytIEI0Dqmv_Gnw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2F8VTNg4tiytIEI0Dqmv_Gnw&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3bHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=f3f999e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8VTNg4tiytIEI0Dqmv_Gnw</a><br />\n睇完呢啲野 我試著諗 我地真係要好好好冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有好多激象法我地都中哂計 現場分析判斷唔到<br />\n盡量唔好係明目既地方做啲打淨化香支港那既行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係既話好易比位對家入 拉劇分化<br />\n<br />\n有幾樣我諗過下既議建分享下<br />\n1）我地知啲犬隻cosplay果陣唔鍾意有鏡頭既情況下表露身分 同做越軌既行為（咁我地可唔可以用啲好細型既錄影機or針筒相機 或者扮下啲紅媒記者 等佢地掉以輕心 捉佢痛腳再搞暗黑文宣<br />\n<br />\n2）暗黑文宣 ... <br />\n<br />\n3）出黎發夢既人 搞唔搞到個街站 即時check職業公司 add埋TG 大圈子咁唔比狗挽呢隻遊戲 係細細個學番既Bully<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4）冇啦屌 冷靜啲呀咁多位 唔好以氣做事 勁衝就小心係鬼 多數香港人都好和平 識過既brand3仔都好講義氣同有心<br />\n<br />\nBtw Comment一黎屌9我鬼既人 一係我講得唔中肯一係佢就係鬼 想降低個post既效果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外想同啲mon post狗講 提出黎既野可能一直做緊可能plan緊去做可能未來會做 醒醒定定 唔好行差踏錯 你仲有好大前途傢垃圾廢狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n後補職業證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5943a007a4bd32c4cca0b7942260fc71139316d","tid":1471021,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f069a70e0f9e422127e57661b80e4050f1c5de76","tid":1471021,"uid":285274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"自推廿次"},{"pid":"3efe45ccafaf47eb5807ec0e332ccaacacdd25b7","tid":1471021,"uid":187489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"1. 唔好扮記者<br />\n<br />\n2. 偷拍俾自己人誤會又出事"},{"pid":"5209489c5eefcee1d14d3e30db0105dec4588ef7","tid":1471021,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"一搞機場 政府就出招拆 好明顯機場係弱點 大家對準黎打"},{"pid":"be4b0ee335d6036287fa437718490703adae9cc1","tid":1471021,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"818<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EB6XTMfWkAAh-f9?format=png&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEB6XTMfWkAAh-f9%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dsmall&h=67aad76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=019344f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-s